se.cbb.jprime.prm

Class DoubleAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.cbb.jprime.prm.DoubleAttribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<ProbAttribute>, ContinuousAttribute, ProbAttribute

    public class DoubleAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
implements ContinuousAttribute
    Defines a probabilistic double PRM attribute, either bounded or unbounded. The attribute automatically adds itself to its PRM class.

    Joel Sj√∂strand.

        public DoubleAttribute(java.lang.String name,
               PRMClass prmClass,
               boolean isLatent,
               int initialCapacity,
               ProbAttribute.DependencyConstraints dependencyConstraints,
               RealInterval interval)
        Constructor for bounded or unbounded double range.
        Parameters:
        name - attribute's name. Should be unique within PRM class.
        prmClass - PRM class this attribute belongs to.
        isLatent - true if hidden or unknown.
        initialCapacity - initial capacity for attribute entities.
        dependencyConstraints - dependency structure constraints.
        interval - the valid range of values.
